cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS

This paper discusses training methods for quantized neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of neural networks in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) is also mentioned. Additionally, the paper explores the behavior of these algorithms for non-convex problems, which relates to optimization (cs.NE) and the theoretical analysis of algorithms (cs.DS).
